{"id": 1268, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得郭敬明为什么要哭？", "description": "“是不是因为我叫郭敬明，所以做什么都是错的？是不是只有我死了，你们才不会骂《爵迹》？”……小四哭了，你怎么看？（题图来自：Andrés Hernández）", "record_count": 7300, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161010105413Vi1XbOtRaQ0kGuxp.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-10T03:06:38Z", "options": [{"id": 122368, "content": "你死了我们还是会骂爵迹啊。。。好歹也算知识份子了这样转移矛盾真的好么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695006}, {"id": 122624, "content": "哭吧，小婊砸～", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776545}, {"id": 124416, "content": "别骂了，毕竟他为《爵迹》能火炒作的也挺费心的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796279}, {"id": 125440, "content": "看了一次小时代，从此跟郭敬明三个字绝缘", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 781998}, {"id": 122369, "content": "谁叫你这么拜金", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779266}, {"id": 122625, "content": "烂片不被骂，你让好片的面子往哪放", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789693}, {"id": 123137, "content": "据说各大平台有大号被盗给爵迹打五星。呵呵哒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 765956}, {"id": 122626, "content": "是，快去吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776931}, {"id": 122371, "content": "当年的粉丝要为自己曾经喜欢的东西买单一辈子吗？那小蝌蚪找妈妈应该全国人民来看呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788946}, {"id": 122627, "content": "烂片不被骂，你让好片的面子往哪放", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789693}, {"id": 122372, "content": "别哭，毕竟你还有钱陪你啊?", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725781}, {"id": 122628, "content": "可怜人，可恨人，可悲人", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734018}, {"id": 122373, "content": "抄就是抄，不要把观众读者当成白痴。哭没用，没有能耐就别折腾。恬不知耻的宣传抄袭的作品的时候，我想很多人都跟我一样感到耻辱，更该掉眼泪的是我们这些观众读者才对。", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789196}, {"id": 122629, "content": "不要认为别人对你有意见，而是你的电影太垃圾，还是做回你的老本行吧，好好写作", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789688}, {"id": 122885, "content": "抄了那么多年，总该付出点代价，人品早就透支完了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 771630}, {"id": 123909, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793949}, {"id": 124165, "content": "抄袭的事说的如此的轻描淡写，哭的怎么哗众取宠……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724878}, {"id": 122374, "content": "为啥骂《大圣归来》那么少？为啥也有说《大圣归来》不好的？本身可能有问题，但嘴是长在别人身上的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718825}, {"id": 122630, "content": "可怜可恨可悲", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734018}, {"id": 122886, "content": "典型的没有搞清楚主要矛盾", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790491}, {"id": 122375, "content": "以为自己是个偶像明星，做什么都有脑残粉买单，结果发现被群嘲", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719672}, {"id": 122631, "content": "是的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758741}, {"id": 122376, "content": "连剧情都没讲清楚的电影你还想求赞美吗…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749198}, {"id": 122632, "content": "我们好好的谈爵迹吧！可是 ta 就是烂片啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742448}, {"id": 122377, "content": "他一直对被骂都无所谓，但是这次被骂还没钱赚，那真是惨哭了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68042}, {"id": 122889, "content": "一部电影说明了自己的品味确实不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 552184}, {"id": 122378, "content": "在你的脑子里已然空荡荡的时候，就不要想着去哄骗别人了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686100}, {"id": 122634, "content": "喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789714}, {"id": 122890, "content": "于是我一个小时代，还有爵迹都没看过也不想看的人，点进来干嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763476}, {"id": 122379, "content": "没有，你只是没有韩姓作家那种导演的能力而已，没什么高不了的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 50876}, {"id": 122635, "content": "臭不要脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657898}, {"id": 122891, "content": "模仿百鸟朝凤的下跪", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790504}, {"id": 123147, "content": "是", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792142}, {"id": 122380, "content": "我不说话，我没看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785081}, {"id": 122636, "content": "我以为他内心应该很强大啊，毕竟小时代123都过来了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759666}, {"id": 122892, "content": "票房不好，电影不好看，哭有什么用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789760}, {"id": 123916, "content": "是，快去吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794861}, {"id": 125452, "content": "演技来凑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793452}, {"id": 122381, "content": "为了炒作爵迹？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614872}, {"id": 122637, "content": "那你死吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 111899}, {"id": 122893, "content": "你写书的时候参考别人的，你拍电影的时候就不参考了么？ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790517}, {"id": 122382, "content": "不哭，站着撸", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501773}, {"id": 122638, "content": "女人哭赖即视感。希望他能成熟地面对质疑，也希望质疑声音多些成熟", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789721}, {"id": 122894, "content": "无言以对…………", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789024}, {"id": 123918, "content": "死不死全凭自己自愿  但是爵迹拍的真是给跪了 尽管主演颜值很高哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794861}, {"id": 133647, "content": "丑人多作怪", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829195}, {"id": 122383, "content": "高二看的爵迹，一直到我大学毕业都没有继续更新，当听说出电影时，我只想呵呵…", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 677020}, {"id": 122639, "content": "“是不是只有我死了”，感觉是他小说里面会出现的对话。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770437}, {"id": 122895, "content": "他的粉丝主要是20以下的人，我们不懂所以也不评论，小四太玻璃心了，有人看就有人骂。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769373}, {"id": 128271, "content": "这爵迹，简直胡弄观众，这特效这剧情，当我们智障，票房不差才怪！这电影假的要命", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150665}]}